name: Nite Ize Dual Carabiner (3 Pack)
description: A set of 3 handy aluminum carabiners for clipping stuff to other stuff. Hang your mug from your pack, attach your keys to your belt or clip your dog to its leash.Made of lightweight solid aluminum with secure stainless steel wire gate closures.Sold as a set of 3 carabiners: one small, one medium, one large.Small carabiner measures 2.3x5x0.7cm and weighs 4g.Medium carabiner measures 3.1x6.9x0.8cm and weighs 9g.Large carabiner measures 4.1x9x1cm and weighs 17g.Not for use where disengagement could result in bodily injury or property damage. Not for climbing.
